title: Ora Sizzles in London As New Boyfriend Travis Barker Keeps it Low Key in LA
text: Rita Ora is quite the sight while heading out for the evening in London on Thursday night (October 8). The 24-year old singer was making her way to the opening of the new London restaurant, Sexy Fish. The platinum blonde beauty oozed glamour with her bold dress and subdued makeup.
